                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <h2>Helping Patients Exchange<br />Limits for Freedom</h2>
                    <p>Peritoneal dialysis (PD) is an at-home therapy option that gives patients the independence to complete treatment at their own convenience, including while they are asleep. This helps limit disruptions to their daily activities and work. </p>
                    <p>In addition to increased independence, at-home PD has demonstrated improvements in mortality rates and in preserving residual renal function when compared with in-center hemodialysis.<sup>1,5</sup></p>
                </div>
